data.description: Priced to sell, this two-story home Is just bursting with potential! This two-story home sits on just over half an acre lot on a street that dead ends into Bennett Field Park and has low township taxes. Inside you will find a first floor with a large kitchen that is plentiful with cabinet space and a large formal dining room. The third bedroom is located on the first floor and would make for a great home office or flex room. First floor laundry with a large mudroom. The primary is located on the second floor with two large closets. Home has a large deck overlooking the large back yard that is perfect for summer entertaining. Call today for your personal showing. Price reflects condition.
